	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you notice, the triangle channel on Zoda's Revenge always does this bongo tap SFX, where the note being played is instantly played one octave higher for like .05 of a second.
<br />
<br />How did they accomplish this?  I doubt they just plained tracked it.  I assume they did some coding to preform this.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


