		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well, they did this by writing some frequency in the triangle channel $400a and $400b, then writing another the frame just after it.
<br />MCK would call this "note enveloppe".
<br />I don't see your point here.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
