		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Star Tropics 2's triangle channel code is kinda wacky too.  Out of all the NSFs in my NSF player, it's the only one that make an attempt to control the volume of the triangle channel by using the $4011 register (carefully ramping it up and down).  I haven't played the cart, but on emulators it seemed hardly even noticeable.

		

